window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Cristina</b></p> <p>Monsters don't hide in the dark.</p> <p>When I met Damian Di Santo in a dark corridor of my family home I knew he was a monster.</p> <p>I was a scared girl. He was already a man.</p> <p>That was when his twisted countdown began.</p> <p>Marked by dead roses and sharp thorns, eight years passed each bringing me closer to becoming his. Until the eve of my 18th birthday.</p> <p>That was the night he returned to claim me.</p> <p><b>Damian</b></p> <p>Circumstance put Cristina on my path. Fate bound her to me.</p> <p>Cristina and I share a common past. A single night that changed the course of our lives.</p> <p>She asked me if I was a monster the night I met her. I am.</p> <p>She's about to learn I'm her monster.</p> <p>Because the countdown that began eight years ago has ended. Her time is up.</p> <p>On the stroke of midnight, she's mine.</p>"; 
